window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>I came to this small town to avenge an attack on my family, to kill the hunter who ruined my brother. I never expected to find my mate. Now that I've found her, there's no possibility I'll return home without Elaine by my side. But she's a human, blind to the world of vampires and I don't know if I can turn her.</p> <p>The hunters want one thing. To kill us all. They know I'm here and they'll stop at nothing to finish what they started with my clan. Being my mate puts Elaine at risk, and I have to do everything within my power to keep her safe.</p> <p>Then I'll claim her.</p> <p>She'll be my mate, my bride, my forever.<br> </p> <p><i>Forever Claimed </i>is a novella featured in the Vampire Brides series. All books in the Vampire Brides series are standalone and can be listened to in any order.</p>"; 
